title: Flash Back: Neal Brennan, Morray and more
itunes:title: Flash Back: Neal Brennan, Morray and more
description:
As the show is away they flashed back to the memorable interivew with Neal Brennan who spoke about Ayahuasca revelations, PC culture, and his new comedy special. Also they flash back to when Charlamagne gave "Donkey of the Day" to a Florida woman for endangering her exes cat during an argument. They also take it back to the first time Morray came to the show.
